<div class="question-card" id="card-6" data-qid="6" data-type="single">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="q-number">Q 07</span>
    <span class="q-tag single">Single Choice</span>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      What is the subnet ID associated with the IPv6 address <strong>2001:DA48:FC5:A4:3D1B::1/64</strong>?
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-6">
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">2001:DA48::/64</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">2001::/64</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">2001:DA48:FC5:A4::/64</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn" data-idx="3">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">D</span>
        <span class="opt-text">2001:DA48:FC5::A4:/64</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="submit-wrap" style="display: none;">
      <button class="submit-btn" id="submit-6" disabled>Submit Answer</button>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation" id="exp-6">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-6"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        The subnet ID for the IPv6 address <strong>2001:DA48:FC5:A4:3D1B::1/64</strong> is:
        <ul>
          <li><strong>2001:DA48:FC5:A4::/64</strong> &mdash; The first 64 bits represent the network and subnet fields.</li>
        </ul>
        The fourth field of hexadecimal digits is the subnet ID, which is <strong>A4</strong> in this case.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pagination-controls">
      <button class="nav-btn" id="prev-6">Previous</button>
      <span class="page-indicator">7 / 7</span>
